# GitHub OAuth App client ID used for the "Sign in with GitHub" device flow.
# Create an OAuth App at https://github.com/settings/developers, enable
# "Device Flow", and paste its Client ID here. Then restart `npm run dev`.
VITE_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=

# Optional: base path that proxies GitHub's device/token endpoints.
# Defaults to "/gh" (see the proxy entry in vite.config.ts).
# VITE_GITHUB_PROXY=/gh
